1
00:00:56,480 --> 00:00:58,440
Master Wang, begin.

2
00:01:39,560 --> 00:01:40,960
What's going on?

3
00:01:43,560 --> 00:01:44,440
Stop!

4
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:50,200
Elder Cao

5
00:01:50,320 --> 00:01:51,120
You...

6
00:01:52,040 --> 00:01:53,120
Why are you here?

7
00:01:53,520 --> 00:01:58,360
Wang Shengchang, how many crimes have you done in Nanwan Town?

8
00:01:58,800 --> 00:02:00,400
My daughter, Shuang'er

9
00:02:00,600 --> 00:02:01,960
My son-in-law, Sanming

10
00:02:02,320 --> 00:02:04,880
And my granddaughter, Yueya

11
00:02:05,200 --> 00:02:07,760
And those innocent girls who died unjustly

12
00:02:07,760 --> 00:02:10,520
Isn't it time to settle these scores?

13
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:13,920
So it was all your doing, you old man.

14
00:02:13,920 --> 00:02:14,920
Wang Shengchang

15
00:02:15,320 --> 00:02:19,520
Even carving you up won't lessen your sins.

16
00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:21,000
I don't kill innocents blindly.

17
00:02:21,440 --> 00:02:25,320
Otherwise, how would I differ from a jerk like you?

18
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:27,760
What do you mean?

19
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:30,000
Are you betraying me too?

20
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:32,320
Yueya, stop now.

21
00:02:32,880 --> 00:02:34,840
Killing him alone is enough.

22
00:02:36,160 --> 00:02:37,880
You're in this together.

23
00:02:39,440 --> 00:02:41,960
Yueya is actually alive.

24
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:45,560
If you're not dead, how could I dare die?

25
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:48,080
Do you like the big gift I gave you?

26
00:02:53,280 --> 00:02:54,520
Good.

27
00:02:54,520 --> 00:02:56,920
I didn't expect this twist.

28
00:02:56,960 --> 00:02:58,120
Since you're here,

29
00:02:58,360 --> 00:03:01,720
No... none of you are leaving.

30
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:03,560
Get them!

31
00:03:06,360 --> 00:03:07,920
No one is to fire!

32
00:03:08,040 --> 00:03:09,680
Don't hurt my son!

33
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:12,360
Yueya

34
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:14,560
Stop killing innocents.

35
00:03:14,680 --> 00:03:15,880
Don't stand in my way.

36
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:17,440
Or I'll kill you too.

37
00:03:25,200 --> 00:03:26,400
You were born a servant.

38
00:03:26,680 --> 00:03:27,720
If not for our Wang family,

39
00:03:27,720 --> 00:03:29,400
you'd have starved to death outside long ago.

40
00:03:29,520 --> 00:03:30,280
What bad luck.

41
00:03:41,200 --> 00:03:43,720
When Mother and I needed you,

42
00:03:44,200 --> 00:03:45,200
where were you?

43
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:46,520
Mother died.

44
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:48,520
You don't deserve to live either.

45
00:03:49,080 --> 00:03:50,080
I'm sorry.

46
00:03:57,160 --> 00:03:57,960
Yueya

47
00:03:58,120 --> 00:03:59,680
Don't stay lost in this obsession.

48
00:04:19,640 --> 00:04:21,360
Wang Yueya, stop now.

49
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:23,280
They are all innocent.

50
00:04:23,520 --> 00:04:25,400
Everyone in the Wang family must die.

51
00:04:25,400 --> 00:04:26,680
That includes you.

52
00:04:26,840 --> 00:04:27,720
Kill!

53
00:04:35,360 --> 00:04:36,160
Zheng Yu

54
00:04:36,280 --> 00:04:37,520
Xu Nan, are you all right?

55
00:04:37,520 --> 00:04:38,240
I'm fine.

56
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:40,040
Fatty, go downstairs and pry the lock open.

57
00:04:40,040 --> 00:04:40,880
Get everyone out.

58
00:04:40,880 --> 00:04:42,240
Xu Nan, go with Fatty.

59
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:43,920
Leave that monster to me.

60
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:44,960
Zheng Yu, be careful!

61
00:04:46,400 --> 00:04:47,200
Let's go, sister-in-law.

62
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:52,720
Kill him!

63
00:05:01,960 --> 00:05:03,280
You want to kill me?

64
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:05,480
It won't be that easy.

65
00:05:06,480 --> 00:05:07,280
Yueya

66
00:05:15,120 --> 00:05:16,680
Kill him for me!

67
00:05:26,760 --> 00:05:29,720
I'm your father!

68
00:05:36,240 --> 00:05:38,000
Who asked you to save me?

69
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:40,160
Yueya

70
00:05:43,440 --> 00:05:45,120
It was Grandfather

71
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:47,120
who wronged you.

72
00:05:48,400 --> 00:05:49,040
You...

73
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:53,000
You must not lose yourself.

74
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:55,600
Don't become

75
00:05:58,480 --> 00:06:02,360
just like them.

76
00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:09,320
Grandfather!

77
00:06:20,960 --> 00:06:22,040
Master!

78
00:06:44,400 --> 00:06:46,480
Now that he has eaten his kin's flesh and blood,

79
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:48,560
he will only grow more frenzied.

80
00:07:03,440 --> 00:07:04,200
Zheng Yu

81
00:07:04,840 --> 00:07:05,640
Xu Nan

82
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:19,600
Let go.

83
00:07:21,200 --> 00:07:22,000
Yueya

84
00:07:22,200 --> 00:07:23,400
This isn't your fault.

85
00:07:23,600 --> 00:07:25,160
Don't give up on yourself so easily.

86
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:27,880
So many innocent people have died already.

87
00:07:28,280 --> 00:07:30,040
Don't throw away your own life too.

88
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:35,240
It's all over.

89
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:37,040
Thank you.

90
00:07:38,520 --> 00:07:40,000
I have no regrets.

91
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:45,000
No, no, Yueya!

92
00:08:16,760 --> 00:08:17,640
Master!

93
00:08:18,400 --> 00:08:20,280
Your disciple chose this place for you.

94
00:08:20,760 --> 00:08:21,960
Are you satisfied with it?

95
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:26,520
I buried your granddaughter here too.

96
00:08:27,120 --> 00:08:29,280
You two can keep each other company.

97
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:31,680
After the Wang family fell,

98
00:08:32,760 --> 00:08:35,680
the people of Nanwan Town lived in peace.

99
00:08:36,240 --> 00:08:37,480
You can rest in peace too.

100
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:43,120
Madam, let's go.

101
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:52,920
My lady

102
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:56,320
Feihu Zai is treating us at his wedding next month

103
00:08:56,360 --> 00:08:58,360
How much should we give?

104
00:08:59,280 --> 00:09:02,200
How much did he give at our wedding?

105
00:09:02,720 --> 00:09:04,080
He was short on money then

106
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:05,760
He only gave one silver dollar

107
00:09:05,920 --> 00:09:08,040
We can't be as stingy as he was

108
00:09:09,120 --> 00:09:11,280
Then let's add a roast chicken
